duties_responsibilities.duty: Conduct business process review and requirements elicitation.
Facilitate executive and diverse groups to topic consensus.
Provide strategic analysis and support to program, division, and agency initiatives.
Work with Agile Scrum, use of JIRA, user story development/validation, sprint planning and backlog grooming.
Deal with contract compliance and contract change notices, specific to requirements specifications.
Practice LEAN principles and support LPI initiatives.
Work with programs governed by state and/or federal regulations.
